@startuml
title The Provenance Tale - how an image earns crucible trust\nSource: RBSYP-chapbook_provenance.adoc (derived presentation of the marker skeleton)

actor "Director Role" as DIR
actor "Retriever Role" as RET
box "committed tree"
participant "Vessel" as VES
participant "Nameplate" as NPL
end box
box "cloud"
participant "Google Cloud Build" as GCB
participant "Mason Role" as MAS
end box
box "GAR"
participant "Lode" as LODE
participant "rbi_hm\n(hallmarks)" as HM
end box

== Movement I - The Reliquary Conclave ==

DIR -> GCB : rbld_conclave
activate GCB
MAS -> LODE : rbld_conclave (mint reliquary Lode, seal vouch)
GCB --> DIR : **touchmark home** (rbf fact)
deactivate GCB
DIR -> VES : rbfl_yoke (RBRV_RELIQUARY, all vessels; commit)

== Movement II - The Local Kludge ==

DIR -> VES : rbfk_kludge (sentry + bottle, local; mints hallmark)
DIR -> NPL : rbrn_drive (composed by kludge; commit)
DIR -> VES : anoint (RBRV_GRAFT_IMAGE; commit)
note right : uncatalogued - surfaced gap:\nno operation quoin to cite

== Movement III - Conjure on the Tether ==

DIR -> GCB : rbfd_ordain (conjure mode)
activate GCB
MAS -> HM : rbfd_build (ark set: image, about, vouch, attestation)
GCB --> DIR : **hallmark home** (build fact)
deactivate GCB
DIR -> HM : rbfv_batch_vouch (SLSA, mode-aware)
RET -> HM : rbfr_summon (vouch-gated pull)
RET -> HM : rbfc_plumb (full: SLSA, SBOM, Dockerfile)
DIR -> HM : Image Rekon (canonical members present)
DIR -> NPL : rbrn_drive (all consumers; commit)
note right : oracle reruns this arc for a bottle vessel\nwith only the drive tail (jupyter case)

== Movement IV - The Airgap Chain ==

DIR -> GCB : rbld_ensconce (forge upstream base)
activate GCB
MAS -> LODE : rbld_ensconce (capture bytes, seal vouch)
GCB --> DIR : **bole touchmark home** (rbf fact)
deactivate GCB
DIR -> VES : rbfl_feoff (elect RBRV_IMAGE_n_ANCHOR; commit)
DIR -> GCB : rbfd_ordain (forge, tethered; builds from Lode anchor)
activate GCB
GCB --> DIR : **forge hallmark home**
deactivate GCB
DIR -> VES : hallmark base handoff (attended; commit)
note right : no operator verb - surfaced gap:\ndirect write of hallmark locator
DIR -> GCB : rbfd_ordain (airgap bottle; resolves inside GAR alone)
activate GCB
GCB --> DIR : **airgap hallmark home**
deactivate GCB
DIR -> NPL : rbrn_drive (commit)

== Movement V - The Bind ==

DIR -> GCB : rbfd_ordain (bind mode; mirror digest-pinned upstream)
activate GCB
GCB --> DIR : **bind hallmark home**
deactivate GCB
RET -> HM : rbfc_plumb (compact)
DIR -> HM : rbfl_jettison (pouch, surgical)
DIR -> HM : Image Rekon (pouch gone, image stands)
DIR -> NPL : rbrn_drive (commit)

== Movement VI - The Graft ==

DIR -> GCB : rbfd_graft (push anointed local image; verdict GRAFTED)
activate GCB
GCB --> DIR : **graft hallmark home**
deactivate GCB
DIR -> HM : rbfl_wrest (layer-digest round trip)
DIR -> HM : rbfl_abjure (terminal hallmark dies)

@enduml
